How to make an stsci_python release
--

Make a branch of stsc_python in the stsci_python repository.

svn checkout the branch

in the root of the checked out branch, run release_tools/branch_externals

perform the svn commands that it displays

** abandon your checked out copy and get a new one **

edit setup.cfg
	change [metadata] version= to the version number of this release
	commit the change

python setup.py sdist

dist/*.tar is the distribution


How to test the release
--

cd to the work directory where you will do the testing

unsetenv PYTHONPATH

irafx

svn checkout release_tools from the release branch 

sh release_tools/testenv
	paste the appropriate commands from what it displayed
		set path, pythonpath
		uninstall
		install setup.py

